T16TD4413E:349b-1: ratna tri sva sti g'a th'a /
T16TD4413E:349b-3: dkon mchog gsum gyi bkra shis kyi tshigs su bcad pa /
T16TD4413E:349b-4: dkon mchog gsum la phyag 'tshal lo //
T16TD4413E:349b-5: che ba'i che mchog ston mchog bla na med //
T16TD4413E:349b-6: chos rje nyi ma rgyal ba'i byin rlabs kyis //
T16TD4413E:349b-7: bdud dang bgegs rigs gnod pa'i dgra zhi ste //
T16TD4413E:349b-8: rtag tu dpal gnas nyin mtshan bkra shis shog / chos nyid bden pa'i chos mchog bla na med //
T16TD4413E:349b-9: dam chos bdud rtsi'i bden pa'i byin rlabs kyis //
T16TD4413E:349b-10: nyes pa'i skyon bral dge tshogs rnams 'phel ba //
T16TD4413E:349b-11: rtag tu dpal gnas nyin mtshan bkra shis shog / dge 'dun yon tan rin chen dpal 'bar ba //
T16TD4413E:349b-12: rgyal sras phan mdzad bden pa'i byin rlabs kyis //
T16TD4413E:349b-13: nyon mongs sdug bsngal gdung ba'i dgra zhi ste //
T16TD4413E:349b-14: rtag tu dpal gnas nyin mtshan bkra shis shog / tshangs dang lha dbang srung ma'i byin rlabs kyis //
T16TD4413E:349b-15: phan mdzad lha yi bkra shis gnas gyur te //
T16TD4413E:349b-16: bde legs bsam pa yid bzhin 'grub pa dang //
T16TD4413E:349b-17: tshe ring nad med bde skyid ldan par shog / dkon mchog gsum gyi bkra shis kyi tshigs su bcad pa bcom ldan 'das kyis khyim bdag des pa la gsungs pa rdzogs so /
T16TD4413E:349b-19: // / rgya gar gyi mkhan po dzi na mi tra dang /
T16TD4413E:349b-20: zhu chen gyi lo ts'a ba bande ye shes sdes bsgyur cing zhus te gtan la phab pa'o /
